    "The dynamic retrieval of information from knowledge bases during the inference phase allows RAG to change what a pretrained language model knows, preventing the model from being retrained with new documents, and finally, accessing and extracting up-to-date information and then use them to produce the results (RIEDEL et al., 2020)."
